<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV105">
<l>maṇṇaiyuṇṭu miḻntupiṉṉi rantukoṇṭa ḷantumaṇ</l>
<l>kaṇṇuḷalla tillaiyeṉṟu veṉṟakāla māyiṉāy</l>
<l>paṇṇaiveṉṟa viṉcolmaṅkai koṅkaitaṅku paṅkayak</l>
<l>kaṇṇaniṉṉa vaṇṇamalla tillaiyeṇṇum vaṇṇamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who are Time, who—swallowing and spitting out the earth, then begging for</l>
<l rend="indent">and acquiring [it],</l>
<l>and measuring [it]—conquered [the worlds] thinking, ‘The earth will not exist unless</l>
<l rend="indent">[it is] under [my] sight!’</l>
<l>O lotus-eyed [Lord] who rests upon the breasts of the lady with sweet words</l>
<l rend="indent">that vanquish melodies!</l>
<l>There is no other form to contemplate other than Your form!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
